 />\n中學雞個陣睇完都唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後悶得滯就無再深究<br />\n難得就黎完sem  睇下再戰多次會唔會又明多dd<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50eaa68ea525ee2cd991e309b125a9bb7f99615","tid":201362,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>UM會唔會好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超野雞</blockquote><br />\n對比世界出名既大學就當然及唔上，不過對比本地佢都算top</blockquote><br />\n巴係打中意中文 所以先簡中文系? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入學前既諗法就係 其他系好討厭，只有中文唔討厭<br />\n入學後就深深愛上中文，中文改變左我成個人同埋諗法，令我接觸到佛，一切皆空既真理"},{"pid":"b3469afe41b167925e11cc67f7b1be17dbe09e49","tid":201362,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中文grad左，有乜好問其實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺中文系既人比較純啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺  比起讀工商、傳抽既學生 中文人的確純好多！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靜係中文同英文都爭好遠<br />\n<br />\n多唔多同學執筆忘字，或者成日寫錯字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de3b284e35129c928afb91b0d1bdd97fd8d4cb5","tid":201362,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>UM會唔會好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超野雞</blockquote><br />\n對比世界出名既大學就當然及唔上，不過對比本地佢都算top</blockquote><br />\n巴係打中意中文 所以先簡中文系? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入學前既諗法就係 其他系好討厭，只有中文唔討厭<br />\n入學後就深深愛上中文，中文改變左我成個人同埋諗法，令我接觸到佛，一切皆空既真理</blockquote><br />\n中國古時思常大唔大程度上受佛教影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得道教, 佛教 兩者中心思想好近<br />\n兩者既念法都好有趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265a060c8f13fe61f10e59e424864701ea88c851","tid":201362,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"UM中文系真係垃圾中嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"7d6ac33a5f9d42130a39e65aa39c7028b56977e0","tid":201362,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>UM會唔會好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超野雞</blockquote><br />\n對比世界出名既大學就當然及唔上，不過對比本地佢都算top</blockquote><br />\n巴係打中意中文 所以先簡中文系? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入學前既諗法就係 其他系好討厭，只有中文唔討厭<br />\n入學後就深深愛上中文，中文改變左我成個人同埋諗法，令我接觸到佛，一切皆空既真理</blockquote><br />\n中國古時思常大唔大程度上受佛教影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得道教, 佛教 兩者中心思想好近<br />\n兩者既念法都好有趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國古時思想 以道家為多，係啊 佢地兩個理念都好相似，但其實講到尾都係有點不同，不過我地其實都唔洗咁執著呢個問題，以順其自然為養身之道"